org.grouplens.grapht.reflect

Class MockSatisfaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.grouplens.grapht.reflect.MockSatisfaction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Satisfaction

    public class MockSatisfaction
extends Object
implements Satisfaction
    MockSatisfaction is a simple implementation of Satisfactions for certain types of test cases. It can be configured by its constructors, although Satisfaction.makeInstantiator(Map, LifecycleManager) always returns the same provider.
    Author:
    GroupLens Research
